
'''= free open-source software for local food networks: groups of farmers who pool and distribute their food to groups of customers.'''

URL = http://foodnetworksoftware.org

=Directory=

Via Bob Haugen:

Demo version: 
https://github.com/bhaugen/foodnetwork

New version for a Nova Scotia group that has not gone live yet:
https://github.com/bhaugen/nova

The Nova version adds some social-networking features between farmers and their customers (mostly restaurants), and allows farmers to set their own pay prices.

The underlying framework, https://docs.djangoproject.com/ is multilingual, but nobody has done the translations for either of those projects.


